{"tid":627530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊面臨全球最大淡倉 頭寸達50.1億美元","createTime":"2018-04-13T04:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T05:22:17.000Z","uid":99493,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69f515d586457df9f2465040c7cce5d0368b1899","tid":627530,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"騰訊（700）近期股價大幅波動，與此同時已建立龐大淡倉頭寸，據《彭博》匯編的數據，針對騰訊的淡倉頭寸價值50.1億美元，這是全球公開披露的最大空倉之一，是由摩根大通代表一眾未披露身份的客戶持有。與此同時，摩通的客戶也直接持有估計價值1,870億美元的騰訊股份，屬於其主要股東之列。"},{"pid":"652e45c61c2b5304837c7b4e250a0bab5a1ec97c","tid":627530,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔玩啦比番d錢我"},{"pid":"41d5ce27d73078e421d8b2b6cc83518b032e2289","tid":627530,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"報乜撚牙"},{"pid":"0cce3e60442c98ee96f5f57e588c0f9d8d6d9184","tid":627530,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"一早沽空完啦"}]}